{"tid":710294,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"香港到底仲有咩影評人值得留意?","createTime":"2018-06-20T15:24:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-13T00:42:02.000Z","uid":188543,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"244fd1e78342632c0c74fe5c7a1a0b9161a68ab2","tid":710294,"uid":188543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T15:24:42.000Z","msg":"個D咩講鏟片港產不打同舒琪黨就算鳩數啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbe073710fb75f75691c59ed6aac420d12f43e85","tid":710294,"uid":22898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T15:39:20.000Z","msg":"依加啲影評除左會講個故事有深度以外，仲會真係評電影咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d6c86477a87e92e1aceaf72d1f0429dbc8cb9c3","tid":710294,"uid":83949,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T15:55:51.000Z","msg":"馮家明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23328afe891659d8c4472614ba06b037408e56e0","tid":710294,"uid":159266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T15:59:45.000Z","msg":"有邊d人屬於舒琪黨?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71b5145f3f910b705e08dd96a3b8c6e4e74e28cf","tid":710294,"uid":179409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"244fd1e78342632c0c74fe5c7a1a0b9161a68ab2","tid":710294,"uid":188543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T15:24:42.000Z","msg":"個D咩講鏟片港產不打同舒琪黨就算鳩數啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T16:41:13.000Z","msg":"十幾年前嘅登徒係OK<br />\n唔係一味講套戲超好睇或者超垃圾<br />\n真係講到戲入面一啲導演想表達<br />\n而好多觀眾留意唔到嘅細節<br />\n仲會由導演同編劇角度分析點解會拍嗰套戲<br />\n點解要講某啲對白或者拍某啲Scene<br />\n有咩意思都會嘗試分析返出嚟<br />\n真係令到聽眾對每套戲嘅感受加強<br />\n教聽眾點樣欣賞每部電影<br />\n而唔係好簡單分類好唔好睇<br />\n跟住喪讚或者喪恥笑<br />\n但而家睇佢啲片都已經唔得<br />\n可能年紀大<br />\n都無咩心機做影評"},{"pid":"a1a9461473d41b7ef5629cdc5afd462b9c15a268","tid":710294,"uid":179409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T16:58:19.000Z","msg":"近年真係諗唔起<br />\n報紙影評都係嗰幾位<br />\n至於網上影評電台<br />\n以前都聽過幾個<br />\n但而家全部都無聽<br />\n<br />\n好似《後巷電影院》、《咬蔗幫》<br />\n啲主持畀我感覺係好唔尊重電影<br />\n做節目態度好傲慢<br />\n好似世上所有電影都係垃圾咁滯<br />\n無咩可聽角度<br />\n仲有《影畫春秋》都算長壽<br />\n不過幾位主持成日唔做功課<br />\n啲戲嘅內容講到錯漏百出<br />\n評論細節都係求求其其<br />\n少少分析都無<br />\n之前請過某客席嘉賓做幾集<br />\n啲內容差到不堪<br />\n嗰位仁兄根本連點欣賞電影都未識<br />\n只係會講「商業片係咁架啦」呢類低能影評<br />\n真係無言"},{"pid":"1f66915dbe28a7e0cad889abe876db13555aa450","tid":710294,"uid":30708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T19:15:35.000Z","msg":"關勁松 阿里安"},{"pid":"46053fa8087bf700ea69dde04cfb6bafc8948814","tid":710294,"uid":174654,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T20:17:53.000Z","msg":"石琪：弱智"},{"pid":"88b7dbc910d7c7d3910b27e816507e65f3d48a1d","tid":710294,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T22:02:06.000Z","msg":"香港無留意，最近睇緊Bilibili既「發條張」，有d料到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://space.bilibili.com/17819768/#/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fspace.bilibili.com%2F17819768%2F%23%2F&d=gVBwHMV%2BUKRpFY4WJToIjcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=77c163c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://space.bilibili.com/17819768/#/</a>"},{"pid":"2571c7b8119cedda5201727624e73f4f2ef35d80","tid":710294,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"88b7dbc910d7c7d3910b27e816507e65f3d48a1d","tid":710294,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T22:02:06.000Z","msg":"香港無留意，最近睇緊Bilibili既「發條張」，有d料到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://space.bilibili.com/17819768/#/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fspace.bilibili.com%2F17819768%2F%23%2F&d=gVBwHMV%2BUKRpFY4WJToIjcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=77c163c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://spac